title: Privacy-focused GrapheneOS based upon Android 12L comes to Pixel 6 in latest beta
content:
After news that custom ROM project ProtonAOSP offers Pixel 6 owners the opportunity to run Android 12L ahead of the official stable release, GrapheneOS is the second such ROM to offer the latest build ahead of Google.

The post Privacy-focused GrapheneOS based upon Android 12L comes to Pixel 6 in latest beta appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: GrapheneOS based upon Android 12L is now available in beta to more Made by Google devices including the Pixel 4a 5G through to the Pixel 6.
